OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Lee Anderson comments
OL,4,C'pour fuel on fire of anti-Muslim
OL,5,Chatred'
OL,7,FSadiq Khan has said Prime Minister
OL,8,FRishi Sunak's "deafening silence" is
OL,9,Fcondoning racism and Islamophobia in
OL,10,Fthe wake of Lee Anderson's comments
OL,11,Fabout the London mayor.
OL,13,FOn Friday, the former deputy Tory
OL,14,Fchairman said "Islamists" had "got
OL,15,Fcontrol" of and that the mayor had
OL,16,F"given our capital city away to his
OL,17,Fmates."
