OL,5,Chatred'
OL,7,FITV News understands the Conservative
OL,8,FMP and former Chancellor, Sajid Javid,
OL,9,Fhas privately urged Rishi Sunak to
OL,10,Fwithdraw the whip from Lee Anderson
OL,11,Funless he issues an apology for his
OL,12,Fremarks.
OL,14,FOn Saturday afternoon, it was
OL,15,Fannounced that Mr Anderson has had the
OL,16,FConservative whip suspended 'following
OL,17,Fhis refusal to apologise' for comments
OL,18,Fabout Mr Khan.
