OL,4,C'pour fuel on fire of anti-Muslim
OL,5,Chatred'
OL,7,FResponding to Mr Anderson's comments,
OL,8,Fthe London Mayor said: "These comments
OL,9,Ffrom a senior Conservative are
OL,10,FIslamophobic, are anti-Muslim and are
OL,11,Fracist.
OL,13,F"We've seen over the last two days
OL,14,Fconfirmation that over the last few
OL,15,Fmonths there's been an increase in
OL,16,Fanti-Muslim cases by more than 330%.
OL,18,F"These comments pour fuel on the fire
OL,19,Fof anti-Muslim hatred.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
