OL,5,Chatred'
OL,7,F"I'm afraid the deafening silence from
OL,8,FRishi Sunak and the cabinet is them
OL,9,Fcondoning this racism."
OL,11,FGrant Shapps, the defence secretary,
OL,12,Ftold ITV News that he had not listened
OL,13,Fto the MP for Ashfield's comments, but
OL,14,Fabout Mr Khan.
