OL,7,FIn an appearance on GB News, Mr
OL,8,FAnderson had said: "I don't actually
OL,9,Fbelieve that the Islamists have got
OL,10,Fcontrol of our country, but what I do
OL,11,Fbelieve is they've got control of Khan
OL,12,Fand they've got control of London...
OL,13,FHe's actually given our capital city
OL,14,Faway to his mates."
