OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Lee Anderson comments
OL,4,C'pour fuel on fire of anti-Muslim
OL,5,Chatred'
OL,7,FThe remarks prompted criticism from
OL,8,FLabour and some Conservatives, with
OL,9,Fsenior Tory MP Sir Sajid Javid
OL,10,Fdescribing them as "ridiculous".
OL,12,FBusiness minister Nus Ghani,
OL,13,Fmeanwhile, said the comments were
OL,14,F"foolish and dangerous".
OL,16,FMr Khan added that he believed the way
OL,17,Fthe claims were being handled by the
OL,18,FConservative Party showed a "hierarchy
OL,19,Fwhen it comes to racism".
