OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Lee Anderson comments
OL,4,C'pour fuel on fire of anti-Muslim
OL,5,Chatred'
OL,7,F"I think it's really important to call
OL,8,Fout antisemitism, misogyny, and
OL,9,Fhomophobia, but surely it must also be
OL,10,Fimportant to call out anti-Muslim
OL,11,Fhatred," he said.
OL,13,F"My concern is there will be people
OL,14,Facross the country who are Muslim or
OL,15,Flook like Muslims, who will be really
OL,16,Fconcerned about entering politics,
OL,17,Fbecause if these are the sort of
OL,18,Fcomments that are said against me by a
OL,19,Fsenior Conservative, what chance do
OL,20,Fthey have?"
