OL,7,FThe Muslim Council of Britain said the
OL,8,Fcomments were "disgusting" and
OL,9,Fcriticised the "silence of the party
OL,10,Fin the face of such extremism".
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "In a week where
OL,13,Fwe learn of an explosion in
OL,14,FIslamophobic hate crimes, influential
OL,15,FMPs and a donor to the Conservative
OL,16,FParty are endorsing common talking
OL,17,Fpoints that peddle conspiracy theories
OL,18,Fand Islamophobic tropes of alleged
OL,19,FMuslim takeovers of our country."
